Name: ansible-lint-to-junit-xml
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: Convert ansible-lint outputs to a jUnit valid xml tests result file
Home-page: https://github.com/andreferreirav2/ansible-lint-to-junit-xml
Author: Andre Ferreira
